{
  "texts": [
    "LoKr and LoHa employ Kronecker and Hadamard products to replace the vanilla matrix product, respectively.",
    "DoRA decomposes the pretrained weight into its magnitude and directional components and fine-tunes them separately.",
    "We also notice a very recent concurrent work FLoRA (Si et al., 2024).",
    "Differences between MoSLoRA and FLoRA are as follows: 1) initialization methods and the corresponding motivation:",
    "The motivation of FLoRA is to maintain the structural integrity of the original high-dimensional parameter spaces (i.e., 2D Convolution) by introducing the core spaces."
  ]
}